WHAT PROBLEM IT SOLVES
Replaces “fastest GPU” claims with auditable TFLOPS, TOPS, and bandwidth
formulas. Allows a GIOP-based renderer to predict exactly how many rays
or AI frames it can process per second, and how much power and memory
bandwidth each task consumes. Guarantees deterministic frame times for
virtual production and eliminates guesswork about DLSS 4 performance.

